{"tid":1195330,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"單車遊學團[粵]","createTime":"2019-06-09T15:11:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T16:15:18.000Z","uid":38456,"like":2,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"4c0059f62dcd820e3c57b1321fcd931f1e7f7e9c","tid":1195330,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T15:11:08.000Z","msg":"單車遊學團[粵]     <br />\n<br />\n勇於接受挑戰的藝人麥明詩、潘梓鋒聯同慈善機構理事王德志、龔朗賢組成「單車遊學團」，以踏單車方式籌款，為柬埔寨小村落擴建校舍，改善學生的讀書環境。整理好戰車與裝備之後，單車團找來香港單車隊前代表胡健燊協助特訓，挑戰登上大帽山。面對艱巨的山路，他們的決心不禁動搖，最終能否克服難關？出發當日，團員們喜獲家人、圈中好友親臨打氣，信心大增。隨着鳴槍聲響起，單車團正式展開28天長征，從太平山頂向着柬埔寨進發！"},{"pid":"75c09b7d594747c9b7b97e30021ecf17fdc8f947","tid":1195330,"uid":21378,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T15:14:38.000Z","msg":"11點先做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;.......咁辛苦都好少人睇."},{"pid":"2038f8496f55f6982734790934ce5bb5acbf179d","tid":1195330,"uid":192307,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T15:15:01.000Z","msg":"等咗你好耐...以為你唔開"},{"pid":"dc622129dee74503a3cdea1f03906d3363afc809","tid":1195330,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"2038f8496f55f6982734790934ce5bb5acbf179d","tid":1195330,"uid":192307,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T15:15:01.000Z","msg":"等咗你好耐...以為你唔開"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T15:15:39.000Z","msg":"一早開左個英文。無人知"},{"pid":"9489f3f0e9aaaa0bd95a07e65243fc0ddd19d301","tid":1195330,"uid":192307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc622129dee74503a3cdea1f03906d3363afc809","tid":1195330,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"2038f8496f55f6982734790934ce5bb5acbf179d","tid":1195330,"uid":192307,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T15:15:01.000Z","msg":"等咗你好耐...以為你唔開"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T15:15:39.000Z","msg":"一早開左個英文。無人知"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T15:16:30.000Z","msg":"下次推下~"},{"pid":"a70ef526467114dd8b4ddce734fc990